data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Spencer, Oklahoma. This cozy 3 bedroom two bath home is ideal for first-time buyers or those looking for a comfortable and convenient place to settle down. The home features a spacious living room that flows seamlessly into the dining room and kitchen, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The home also makes the most of every inch of space, offering plenty of storage and functionality. The fridge is even staying with the home. You will love the charming curb appeal and the amazing fenced in yard, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Plus, you will enjoy the friendly community and the nearby park, where you can have fun and make memories. Don’t miss this opportunity to own this wonderful home.
